Notification Service

Packages 
Package Description
org.alljoyn.ns
The package includes API classes of the Notification service which are used to send and receive notification messages
org.alljoyn.ns.commons
The package includes generic classes that are used by other packages of the Notification service
org.alljoyn.ns.nativeplatform
The package includes classes with the platform dependent logic.
